des:\n- Use of the iOS app\n- Project management\n- Clients & hourly rate\n- Tags (labels)\n- Dashboard\n- Enhanced history\n- Detailed reports\n- Save, print or download your data\n- More at tomatoid.com/@/features\n\nPremium membership is FREE for:\n- Students (ISIC card needed)\n- Teachers\n- Non-profits & charities\n- Anyone who will share the app with friends\n- More at tomatoid.com/@/pricing\n\n- - -\n\nTomatoid is developed by freelance developer Petr Nagy.\nThe development started in 2013. First version was released in 2014.\n\ntomatoid.com\npetrnagy.cz', '/upload/logo/[logo]2cb6bfa8146d8c5e2b2a415fe9288317_600x600.png', '/upload/logo/[tn]2cb6bfa8146d8c5e2b2a415fe9288317_300x300.png', '0.0000', '0', '2018-02-18 16:56:16', '2018-02-19 13:06:03', '2018-02-19 13:06:03', null), ('5', '2', 'Evernote', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet 2', 'https://www.evernote.com', null, null, null, null, null, '/upload/logo/[logo]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_300x300.png', '/upload/logo/[tn]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_150x150.png', '0.0000', '1', '2018-02-20 17:09:26', '2018-02-20 17:29:25', '2018-02-20 17:29:25', '2018-02-20 17:29:25'), ('6', '2', 'Evernote', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet 3', 'https://www.evernote.com', null, null, null, null, null, '/upload/logo/[logo]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_300x300.png', '/upload/logo/[tn]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_150x150.png', '0.0000', '1', '2018-02-20 17:32:12', '2018-02-20 17:32:35', '2018-02-20 17:32:35', null), ('7', '2', 'Evernote', 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet', 'https://www.evernote.com', null, null, null, null, null, '/upload/logo/[logo]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_300x300.png', '/upload/logo/[tn]09da79c084c709882f673d02c919436a_150x150.png', '0.0000', '1', '2018-02-20 18:05:09', '2018-02-20 19:21:13', '2018-02-20 19:21:13', null), ('8', '1', 'Tomatoid', '3v1 Pomodoro timer, time tracker & task manager', 'https://www.tomatoid.com', null, null, null, null, null, '/upload/logo/[logo]f7e95b428ebaa78ee06c3e14406cd07b